        "description": "Superstring spectrum in 10d Minkowski, as well as simple toroidal and orbifold compactifications.  T-duality, D-branes, tree amplitudes.  Construct some simple unified models of particle physics.  Motivate the 10- and 11-dimensional supergravities.  Simple supergravity solutions and use these to explore some aspects of AdS/CFT duality.",
