        "description": "This course is a practicum course associated with Psych 614A \"Theory and Application in Couples' Therapy\".  This second practicum experience will involve closely supervisoed assessment and intervention with couples relationship distress.  Only students in the Clinical Psychology program are permitted to take this course.",
